data.description: Great property located in the greater eastside of St Paul. The main level features 3 bedrooms, a living room with a fireplace a lot lots of storage. Eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, Full bath, and primary 1/2 bath. The lower level has 2nd living room with a laundry room featuring a toilet and laundry tub. Additonal storage in the utility room. Partial fenced back yard and 2 car garage. Handicap ramp out front.
